00:41:29.780 --> 00:41:32.389
It's something that
both sides of the aisle

00:41:32.389 --> 00:41:34.180
ought to be able to
agree on at this point,

00:41:34.180 --> 00:41:35.160
is stop subsidizing.

00:41:35.160 --> 00:41:37.210
And what better time
to stop subsidizing

00:41:37.210 --> 00:41:39.980
